::Zardus/DevilDuer::

Zardus frowns, looking at Cybershark. "Nonetheless, your internal 
scanners could have picked up something. Go to the CR chambers, it'll 
only take a second. Then I'll give you your mission."

He turns his head, looking at Lady Hawk. "I'll need that for some 
research," he says. He was starting to get a bit annoyed by this
femm, 
but he didn't let it show.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer walks up to the Alliance base's entrance (Scorpina
hopefully 
following him).

"Here we are," he says triumphantly as he sets Scorpina to be 
recognized by the defences, "The Alliance Base!"
